- name: "Spec Example 2.13. In literals, newlines are preserved"
  from: "http://www.yaml.org/spec/1.2/spec.html#id2759963"
  tags: spec scalar literal comment
  yaml: "# ASCII Art\n--- |\n  \\//||\\/||\n  // ||  ||__\n"
